{
  "lifecycles": [
    {
      "id": "networking-direct-connect-routing",
      "service": "networking/direct-connect",
      "enabled": true,
      "heavy": true,
      "_note": "Direct Connect + routing-rule CRUD (Wave 2, NOT runtime-proven, HEAVY/billable). A direct-connect attaches to a base VPC: the session-shared VPC (adopt:vpc, per knowledge/vpc-scheduling-strategy.md — does NOT self-create a VPC). Then: create-dc -> get/set-dc, create-routing-rule -> delete-routing-rule, delete-dc. All dc/routing-rule writes are one optional 'dc' group so a bad body skips only this family (cleaned up children-first). Bodies from data/api_docs.json request_example. create-dc returns $.direct_connect.id; create-routing-rule returns $.routing_rule.id (both soft-captured; dependent steps reference {direct_connect_id}/{routing_rule_id} -> real chain on success, literal-but-norm-matching on 4xx so coverage still records). NOTE: the docs createdirectconnect example sends tags as a STRINGIFIED list (\"[{'key':...}]\") which is almost certainly a doc bug; we send a proper JSON list [] (the engine merges owner tags). bandwidth=1 (Gbps?) is a docs guess; routing-rule destination_type=ON_PREMISE with destination_cidr; destination_resource_id omitted (we have no on-premise resource) which may 4xx -> optional/tolerant. Covers all 5 direct-connect WRITE ops: POST /v1/direct-connects, PUT /v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}, DELETE /v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}, POST /v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}/routing-rules, DELETE /v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}/routing-rules/{routing_rule_id}.",
      "steps": [
        {
          "name": "create-vpc",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/vpcs",
          "json": {
            "name": "regrvpc{unique}",
            "description": "API regression dc",
            "cidr": "10.124.0.0/20",
            "tags": []
          },
          "capture": {"vpc_id": "$.vpc.id"},
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202],
          "cleanup": {"method": "DELETE", "path": "/v1/vpcs/{vpc_id}", "service": "vpc"},
          "adopt": "vpc"
        },
        {
          "name": "wait-vpc",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/vpcs/{vpc_id}",
          "expect_status": [200],
          "poll": {"field": "$.vpc.state", "until": ["ACTIVE", "CREATED", "RUNNING"], "timeout": 300, "interval": 10}
        },
        {
          "name": "create-direct-connect",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/direct-connects",
          "group": "dc",
          "optional": true,
          "json": {
            "bandwidth": 1,
            "description": "API regression suite",
            "firewall_enabled": true,
            "firewall_loggable": true,
            "name": "regrdc{ualpha}",
            "tags": [],
            "vpc_id": "{vpc_id}"
          },
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202, 400, 403, 404, 409, 422],
          "capture_soft": {"direct_connect_id": "$.direct_connect.id"},
          "cleanup": {"method": "DELETE", "path": "/v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}", "service": "direct-connect"}
        },
        {
          "name": "get-direct-connect",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}",
          "group": "dc",
          "optional": true,
          "expect_status": [200, 400, 403, 404]
        },
        {
          "name": "set-direct-connect",
          "method": "PUT",
          "path": "/v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}",
          "group": "dc",
          "optional": true,
          "json": {"description": "API regression suite (updated)"},
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202, 400, 403, 404, 409, 422]
        },
        {
          "name": "create-routing-rule",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}/routing-rules",
          "group": "dc",
          "optional": true,
          "json": {
            "description": "API regression suite",
            "destination_cidr": "11.11.11.0/24",
            "destination_type": "ON_PREMISE"
          },
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202, 400, 403, 404, 409, 422],
          "capture_soft": {"routing_rule_id": "$.routing_rule.id"},
          "cleanup": {"method": "DELETE", "path": "/v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}/routing-rules/{routing_rule_id}", "service": "direct-connect"}
        },
        {
          "name": "list-routing-rules",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}/routing-rules",
          "group": "dc",
          "optional": true,
          "expect_status": [200, 400, 403, 404]
        },
        {
          "name": "probe-dc-reads",
          "probe_reads": {"direct_connect_id": "{direct_connect_id}"}
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-routing-rule",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}/routing-rules/{routing_rule_id}",
          "group": "dc",
          "optional": true,
          "destructive": true,
          "expect_status": [200, 202, 204, 400, 403, 404, 409],
          "retry_on_status": [409],
          "retries": 6,
          "retry_interval": 15
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-direct-connect",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/direct-connects/{direct_connect_id}",
          "group": "dc",
          "optional": true,
          "destructive": true,
          "expect_status": [200, 202, 204, 400, 403, 404, 409],
          "retry_on_status": [409],
          "retries": 8,
          "retry_interval": 15
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-vpc",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/vpcs/{vpc_id}",
          "expect_status": [200, 202, 204, 409, 404],
          "destructive": true,
          "retry_on_status": [409],
          "retries": 40,
          "retry_interval": 30,
          "adopt": "vpc"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
